保密要求 Confidentiality Requirements
绝    密：未经传音控股书面授权，不得复制、存储、引用或传播文件的任何片断。
机    密：复制、存储、引用或传播文件的任何片断，需经部门主管授权。
内部公开：仅限公司内部使用，如需分享到公司外部，需经部门主管授权。
外部公开：无保密要求。

TOP SECRET: Any fragment herein shall not be copied, saved, quoted or spread without TRANSSION HOLDINGS' written authorization.
CONFIDENTIAL: Any fragment herein shall not be copied, saved, quoted or spread without department manager's authorization.
INTERNAL USE: For internal use only. It shall not be shared to outside without department manager's authorization.
PUBLIC: Open.
1. 请基于贵司已通过的技术方案，填写黄色表头部分；请根据 Route和airline来报价；“1st Round Access” 为“Y”的线路，表示贵司在本轮具备投标资格，可以投标；请不要删减或增加行数；
data.col_12:
1. Please quote in sheet《Quotation》in YELLOW column, base on your technical solution approved by Transsion;please quote according to Route and airline.
We also identify your qualification for each routes in column “1st Round Access”,  "Y" means that your company is qualified to quote in this round and you can quote.

data.col_0: 2. 报价有效期 20250501 至 20260430，以实际起飞日期计费，而不是提单日期；
data.col_12: 2 Quotation should be valid from 20250501 to 20260430 based on actual departure date but NOT AWB date. Indian Region might be effective in advance.

data.col_0:
3.  线路设置了淡季报价和旺季报价，时效要求相同，请确保方案满足时效要求；旺季时间固定为10月1日~次年1月31日，切换前双方协商邮件确认，最终解释权归传音所有。
请谨慎考虑报价，如毁约传音有权直接取消下一年参标资格。
data.col_12:
3.Please pay attention to service standard. Slack season rate and peak season are under same T/T requirement;
 The peak season is with fix period from Oct 1st to Jan 31th of next year. Before switching of Slack and Peak season, we will have mail confirmation with mutual agreement but Transsion reserve the rights of final interpretation.  Pls be cautious quoting for the bid, if any breaches of the contract from your side Transsion reserve the rights of direct canceling bidding qualifications for next year.

data.col_0: 4. 报价仅保留两位小数点；切勿带公式！
data.col_12: 4 Please only reserve TWO decimal digits for your quotation.Do not bring formulas！

data.col_0: 5. 报价币种为USD，不含大陆增值税。后续执行过程中，如有异常费用发生，且币种不为USD，汇率按照对账当月中国银行第一个工作日的中行折算价进行结算
data.col_12: 5. Currency is USD, China mainland VAT is exclusive.If there are sundry items in further operation, which currency is not USD, The settlement shall be made according to the bank of China converted price on the first working day of the month of bill reconciliation.

data.col_0: 6. 报价应包含空运费，起运港操作费，安检费和燃油等全部费用，报All-in Rate；但不含大湾区（除澳门）提货费和香港交仓登记费，大湾区（除澳门）为传音自送，香港交仓登记费由传音派送司机交仓时支付现金。(传音香港交仓登记费标准为HKD260/车)
data.col_12: 6. Quotation pls submit all in rate ( include Air freight/ Origin handling charges/FSC/Inspection fee), Transsion will handle pickup and deliver to LSP warehouse for Greater Bay area (except MFM),  no pickup fee & registration fee to include in all in rate. The HKG W/H registration fee is paied by Transsion driver by cash on-  site. (HKG W/H registration fee HKD260/truck per Transsion standard)

data.col_0: 7. 香港、大陆、澳门起运燃油附加费根据各自航空公司标准，计入All-in Rate。
data.col_12: 7. The FSC per airline standard for HKG/Mainland/MFM origin port should inclduded in All in rate

data.col_0: 8. 如涉及香港本地提送货，请按传音支付标准USD0.04/KG执行。
data.col_12: 8. Subject to pickup service for HKG local pickup & delivery, the pickup charge is USD0.04/KG per Transsion standard rate.

data.col_0: 9. 内地起运的方案，需物流商代传音安排出口报关，报关资料电子版由传音关务组提供；报关代理费标准：首页 USD28/单，加页 USD8/页；
data.col_12: 9.  For the shipment ex-Mianland China ，we require your good company to arrange export custom declaration for Transsion，declaration documents provided by Transsion. Shipment ex-Mainland China Customs clearance fee standard: USD28/Bill for first page，Continued page USD8/page;

data.col_0: 10. 如遇散箱出货的订舱，我司以拖盘缠围膜的形式送至贵司仓库，要求贵司免费安排拆围膜和卸拖盘，拖盘我司不需要回收，请自行处理；
data.col_12: 10. If shipment packed by cartons might be delivered to your warehouse by pallet，please remove protection film and pallet by yourself (for free of course)，Transsion will not recycle pallets and films.
